text: Native could mean: *Native person, see Indigenous peoples *Native (ecology), an animal or plant species that comes from a given place *In computing, native software is software that is written for a specific processor (see native on Wiktionary) *Native (processing), a CPU processing system *Native (comics), a character in the X-Men comics universe *Native (band), a contemporary French R&B; band Category:Basic English 850 words
title: Native
